title: Breaking Down ‘The Mandalorian’ Season 2 Finale With Mallory Rubin
description:
Chris and Andy are joined by Mallory Rubin to break down the Season 2 finale of ‘The Mandalorian.’ They talk about their initial takeaways from the episode (1:00), what the big reveal means for the series (14:24), and where the show, and the franchise, goes from here (34:23).

Hosts: Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald
Guest: Mallory Rubin
